cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM 

This paper focuses on computer vision tasks related to object detection and tracking using Unmanned Aerial Vehicles (UAVs). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, since UAVs are mobile robots, the paper may also belong to cs.RO (Robotics and Control). The use of state-of-the-art algorithms suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the annotation of attributes such as weather condition and flying altitude suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia).
